# convex/_generated is committed so Vercel builds don't depend on codegen
# running successfully during `convex deploy --cmd`. Regenerate locally
# via `npx convex dev` (auto) or `npx convex codegen` (one-shot) when
# you change schemas or function signatures, then commit the diff.
